| id       | int(11)     | NO   | PRI | NULL    | auto_increment |
| name     | varchar(30) | YES  |     | NULL    |                |
| password | varchar(15) | YES  |     | NULL    |                |
| mobile   | varchar(15) | YES  |     | NULL    |                |
| address  | varchar(60) | YES  |     | NULL    |                |
| email    | varchar(40) | YES  |     | NULL    |                |
+----------+-------------+------+-----+---------+----------------+
